translated: Bjarne, Gulli Herta, subject teacher, Mrs., Laholm, b. 6/3/93 in Gothenburg to L. Bergqvist and Hilda Nilsson. Married in 1919 to schoolteacher N.J.O. Bjarne. Children: Ingrid b. 1920, married to wholesaler Sven Ahlström, Jönköping, Ulla b. 1921, married to architect Lennart Billgren, Stockholm. Graduated from a private high school in Gothenburg in 1913. Taught at a private Sami school in Laholm, served as acting subject teacher in 1915 and became a regular subject teacher at a lower secondary school in Laholim in 1931.
